select personal_butterfly_aid from cm2account where uid=%1$d
select personal_butterfly_count from cm2account where uid=%1$d
select * from cm2activity as a where a.aid in ( select distinct(b.aid) from cm2butterfly as b where b.bid in ( select distinct(l.bid) from cm2lottery as l where l.uid=%1$d))
select * from cm2butterfly as b where (b.bid in ( select distinct(l.bid) from cm2lottery as l where l.uid=%1$d)) and b.aid=%2$d
select * from cm2catchaction as a where a.uid=%1$d
select b.catched_counter from cm2butterfly as b where b.bid=%1$d
select * from cm2lottery as l where l.uid=%1$d and l.bid=%2$d
select museum_data_updated from cm2account where uid=%1$d
select never_fly_personal from cm2account where uid=%1$d
select * from cm2poi as p where p.aid=%1$d
select * from cm2personalbutterfly as b where (b.lid in ( select distinct(l.lid) from cm2lottery as l where l.uid=%1$d)) and b.aid=%2$d
select butterfly_type from cm2account where uid=%1$d
update cm2account set personal_butterfly_aid=%1$d where uid=%2$d
update cm2account set personal_butterfly_count=%1$d where uid=%2$d
update cm2activity set butterfly_quantity=%1$d where aid=%2$d

ALTER TABLE cm2account ADD butterfly_type INTEGER DEFAULT 0;

ALTER TABLE cm2activity ADD butterfly_list_str TEXT;

ALTER TABLE cm2butterfly ADD throwable INTEGER DEFAULT 0;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2butterfly ( bid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL UNIQUE, aid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, name TEXT NOT NULL, uri1 TEXT, uri2 TEXT, uri3 TEXT, type INTEGER DEFAULT 0, shop_coupon_id TEXT, shop_seller_id TEXT, luckydraw_id TEXT, kaka_privilege_id TEXT, start_date TEXT, expired_date TEXT, slot_idx INTEGER DEFAULT 0, catched_date TEXT, catched_counter INTEGER, kaka_timeinterval REAL DEFAULT 0, kaka_sdate TEXT, kaka_totalqt INTEGER DEFAULT 0, kaka_leftqt INTEGER DEFAULT 0)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2catchaction ( action_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, uid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, action_account TEXT, action_behavior TEXT, action_date TEXT, action_distance TEXT, action_butterflyid TEXT, action_butterfly_title TEXT, action_butterfly_image_url TEXT)
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD catcher_account TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD catcher_id INTEGER DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD collection_points_amount INTEGER DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD latitude REAL DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD longitude REAL DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD oriented_oprice_str TEXT DEFAULT '0';

ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD owner_account TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD owner_id INTEGER DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD personal_content TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD personal_distance TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD personal_photo_url TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD personal_weibo_account TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD store_addr TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD store_name TEXT;
ALTER TABLE cm2lottery ADD store_phone TEXT;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2lottery ( lid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL, global_lid TEXT DEFAULT 0, uid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, bid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, type INTEGER DEFAULT 0, start_date TEXT, expired_date TEXT, logo_uri TEXT, banner_uri TEXT, wap_url TEXT, bonus_amount REAL DEFAULT 0, joke_title TEXT, joke_content TEXT, kaka_name TEXT, kaka_desc TEXT, offline_token TEXT, offline_submit_status INTEGER DEFAULT 0, shop_seller_id TEXT, shop_seller_nick TEXT, shop_name TEXT, shop_discount REAL DEFAULT 0, shop_discount_condition REAL DEFAULT 0, oriented_item_id TEXT, oriented_name TEXT, oriented_price REAL DEFAULT 0, oriented_rate REAL DEFAULT 1, oriented_oprice REAL DEFAULT 0, oriented_status TEXT, oriented_preview_uri TEXT, oriented_seller_id TEXT, oriented_seller_nick TEXT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2personalbutterfly ( bid INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, aid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, lid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL UNIQUE, name TEXT NOT NULL, uri1 TEXT, uri2 TEXT, uri3 TEXT, type INTEGER DEFAULT 0, shop_coupon_id TEXT, shop_seller_id TEXT, luckydraw_id TEXT, kaka_privilege_id TEXT, start_date TEXT, expired_date TEXT, slot_idx INTEGER DEFAULT 0, catched_date TEXT, catched_counter INTEGER, kaka_timeinterval REAL DEFAULT 0, kaka_sdate TEXT, kaka_totalqt INTEGER DEFAULT 0, kaka_leftqt INTEGER DEFAULT 0)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2poi ( pid INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, global_pid TEXT, aid INTEGER DEFAULT 0, lng REAL DEFAULT 0, lat REAL DEFAULT 0, radius REAL DEFAULT 0, title TEXT, desc1 TEXT, desc2 TEXT, wap_url TEXT, logo_uri TEXT)

replace into cm2personalmsg ( msg_type, bid, uid_butterfly_creator, uid_login, uid_msg_from, username_login, username_msg_from, butterfly_image_url, butterfly_distance, msg_time, msg_content) values ('%1$s', %2$d, %3$d, %4$d, %5$d, '%6$s', '%7$s', '%8$s', '%9$s', '%10$s', '%11$s')

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS cm2personalmsg ( msg_id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, msg_type TEXT, bid INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, uid_butterfly_creator INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, uid_login INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, uid_msg_from INTEGER NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, username_login TEXT, username_msg_from TEXT, butterfly_name TEXT, butterfly_image_url TEXT, butterfly_distance TEXT, msg_time TEXT, msg_content TEXT, CONSTRAINT msg_unique_key UNIQUE (bid, uid_login, uid_msg_from, msg_time))
